Rheum Backlog

Rheumatology Backlog

I have now done a first and second audit cycle of the Rheumatology outpatients backlog - based on the status date of the patients on the 17th September (cyc1) and 17th October 2021 (cyc2).

This is the raw data for this - abbreviated to just include the May 2020 - May 2021 period.

The value delta represents the change in patients in the backlog in 1 month, deltaperc represents this number as a percentage of patients in the first cycle (cyc1)

The median percentage of patients removed from the backlog per month is:

## [1] -24.32432
